      "name": "dark-editorial",
      "description": "AI-extracted template from reference design",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Design Conversion</title>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --bg: #000000;\n            --primary: transparent; /* Not explicitly used in this design */\n            --secondary: transparent; /* Not explicitly used in this design */\n            --accent: transparent; /* Not explicitly used in this design */\n            --text: #e0e0e0; /* Light grey for main body text */\n            --text-muted: #a0a0a0; /* Muted grey for header/footer text */\n            --surface: transparent; /* Not explicitly used in this design */\n\n            --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n            --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            background-color: #1a1a1a; /* A slightly different background for the page itself, to distinguish the canvas */\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #app {\n            width: 1080px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background-color: var(--bg);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            padding: 80px; /* Adjust padding to match visual spacing */\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .header-left {\n            font-family: var(--font-sans);\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .header-right {\n            font-family: var(--font-serif); /* Using a serif font for a calligraphic feel */\n            font-size: 28px; /* Adjusted to match visual size */\n            font-weight: 400;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            line-height: 1; /* Ensure no extra line height */\n        }\n\n        .main-content {\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center; /* Vertically center initially */\n        }\n\n        .body-text {\n            font-family: var(--font-serif);\n            font-size: 48px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            color: var(--text);\n            max-width: 700px; /* Adjust max-width to control line breaks */\n            text-align: left;\n            margin: 0; /* Remove default paragraph margin */\n            transform: translateY(-50px); /* Adjust this value to fine-tune vertical position, shifting it slightly upwards */\n        }\n\n        .footer {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-end;\n            width: 100%;\n            font-family: var(--font-sans);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .footer-left, .footer-right {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"app\">\n        <header class=\"header\">\n            <div class=\"header-left\">\n                {{brand_name}}\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"header-right\">\n                <!-- DECORATIVE_TEXT: Stylized characters -->[Decorative Text]\n            </div>\n        </header>\n\n        <main class=\"main-content\">\n            <p class=\"body-text\">\n                {{body}}\n            </p>\n        </main>\n\n        <footer class=\"footer\">\n            <div class=\"footer-left\">\n                <!-- AUTHOR_NAME -->[Author Name]<br>\n                <!-- AUTHOR_HANDLE -->[@authorhandle]\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"footer-right\">\n                \u00a9{{brand_name}} <!-- YEAR -->[YYYY]<br>\n                <!-- WEBSITE_URL -->[www.website.com]\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Lucide icons are not used in this specific design, but the script is included as per requirements. -->\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\"></script>\n    <script>\n        lucide.createIcons();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
